  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350 degrees F.",
    "Sauté onion and garlic in oil until translucent, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add orange zest and ginger root, cook for an additional minute.",
    "Crush the fermented vegetables and mix with tomato paste, juice, salt, and pepper. Stir into the pan.",
    "Transfer mixture to a baking dish, top with beef shin, cover with foil.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes, then uncover and bake for another 10-15 minutes until the beef is cooked through and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Serve hot."
